{"tid":395913,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解深水埗呢個閪站可以咁熱","createTime":"2017-09-11T08:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T18:33:37.000Z","uid":36441,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a237d7ee7daece71e290a688d04e284094cad8c3","tid":395913,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"呢個閪站大堂定月台都好真係一年四季都係咁撚熱架喎 人地露天月台都話淨係夏天熱 仲要個個出口裝曬風閘成個大堂都好似無冷氣咁款 年年加咁多價連通風呢啲咁基本都搞唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fc5d2e84d5587bcaad8d2fc3c93c46e82a0a8a","tid":395913,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84b9075d4ab71aba7cf0a2917fb9b1af45c108c9","tid":395913,"uid":97776,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"年年加1毛<br />\n冷氣年年升1度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f14172c177875e1d43c943ea714f746cb4f020f","tid":395913,"uid":18801,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"去過紅磡未"},{"pid":"1903007550c032a78b7887fd7a46616639dc0327","tid":395913,"uid":41817,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:38:00.000Z","msg":"葵芳呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317bff1c252a77ad5d0e843f233edf0b1cfc71f5","tid":395913,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"紅磡先最熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7077b457c58ed39f462e5d3ec799cd5c3c94a076","tid":395913,"uid":36441,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅磡先最熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅磡無幕門架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要原本都唔預有冷氣 點比"},{"pid":"4227f3ae391b6875c756ec452c3be025111688b3","tid":395913,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過旺角東未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旺角東識企有啲位有冷氣出風位幾凍下 唔似深水埗啲風熱既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋火車站本來都唔預有冷氣啦"},{"pid":"d327e5bf3b5ed24a8a76728f71d64da50b83a9a0","tid":395913,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:18:35.000Z","msg":"北角大堂到a出口"},{"pid":"81e64e7dd5a9e37465d85cd5da2cb098810f165e","tid":395913,"uid":69289,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:52:06.000Z","msg":"紅磡世界級 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然月台樓底高空間又大，但設計幾乎係掘頭路，自然通風根本就冇用<br />\n<br />\n月台啲風扇將返大陸架車大塵廚房啲味散到四圍都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 臭到<br />\n<br />\n早一兩年連大堂同出口啲通道都冇冷氣，啲冷氣機出風口真係得個樣"},{"pid":"96df978e2a9c364956f44a27f91a9d84b54b178a","tid":395913,"uid":137694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"紅磡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adde545f04367fcb2acf4b7b6e1e90feeb085676","tid":395913,"uid":69961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T03:33:24.000Z","msg":"旺角東同紅磡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959fb581d799a14a5d02dd78128fe2cb1c7e5855","tid":395913,"uid":34970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T03:49:35.000Z","msg":"柴灣<br />\n<br />\n次次行完都好似焗桑拿咁"},{"pid":"07575ab1c02ac9c60a6844a547693ba095ce3eb7","tid":395913,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T04:01:53.000Z","msg":"去過柴灣未？"},{"pid":"0a9e536cc831f2e3162e2bdc688292593dbdcd7a","tid":395913,"uid":78188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"葵興 葵芳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a9dab5b2395b64a7496b4fc63672ed2397ddbc","tid":395913,"uid":23423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:45:48.000Z","msg":"啲低級賤民集中地係咁。"},{"pid":"8ee35962278f59fa49eb6c41fc305adff618c189","tid":395913,"uid":59481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"去過大圍未?"},{"pid":"998b06df1a45ed667fffb6152b5365ef4227a4bc","tid":395913,"uid":137694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過大圍未?</blockquote><br />\n大圍反而幾涼喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11de8768805b8e4bf3e8f4a6b08477ddcafaa93d","tid":395913,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"多人就熱架啦，個個站都係咁"},{"pid":"0b7695d3c5dd86954dd45c1b84b674ad7fcdfcc3","tid":395913,"uid":9466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:01:09.000Z","msg":"去過鰂魚涌未？"},{"pid":"e1be349588bc75835369b1b3a94f87c7bee9ec0e","tid":395913,"uid":483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"紅磡成個蒸爐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3746147eeb31ed94c81b125d509f24a4fecf277","tid":395913,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多人就熱架啦，個個站都係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傻啦 深水埗幾點都咁熱 同埋你去下西鐵同東涌線"},{"pid":"3ded7a23d9c017628868fc6816374fd339c81ad1","tid":395913,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":